title: John Sandford - Phantom Prey
description: 2008A widow comes home to her large house in a wealthy, exclusive suburb to find blood everywhere, no body?and her college-aged daughter missing. She&#039;s always known that her daughter ran with a bad bunch. What did she call them?Goths? Freaks is more like it, running around with all that makeup and black clothing, listening to that awful music, so attracted to death. And now this.
